    "ideation": "The 'rewind' emoji is a temporal performance. It represents a reversal of time and causality, characterized by high-speed motion, glitching visual artifacts, and a mechanical pull backwards. The animation sequence treats the face as if it's being sucked into a vacuum on the left. The eyes snap their gaze to the far left immediately, while the mouth becomes a high-frequency jitter simulating the tape-hiss or audio screech of a reversing VCR. The 'glitch' frames use sudden eye-scaling and lid-angle distortions to mimic digital frame-dropping before settling into a fast, rhythmic roll of the mouth wave to show sustained high-speed rewinding. The color palette uses VHS-tracking blues and purples.",
